# CSSLv3 RESEARCH MANIFEST
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# § I> CSSLv3 = novel proprietary hardware-first systems lang
#   co-designed-with LoA-engine ≡ single artifact
# § I> scope: PROPERLY-DISTINCT from CSLv3 (notation) ⊗ CSSL2 (prior attempt)
# § I> research-phase ¬ design-phase-yet
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

§ CONSTRAINTS'hw
  W! target = x86-64.AVX2 + Vulkan1.3.SPIR-V
  W! HW'primary = Intel-12th-14th-gen + Intel-Arc-A770
  N! AVX-512
  W! abstraction-layer + future-HW-portability
  ✓ bootstrap'one-time = existing-lang (throwaway) → self-host ASAP
  W! CSSLv3 + LoA-engine = ONE-artifact
    ∴ lang-primitives ≡ engine-primitives

§ NON-NEGOTIABLE-FEATURES F1..F4
  F1 : autodiff
    W! @differentiable-fn
    W! SDF'normals = O(1) via reverse-mode
    ✓ fix V11-perf-cliff : 10fps → 182fps
  F2 : refinement-types
    W! SDF'Lipschitz-tracking
    W! compile-time thin-feature-warnings
  F3 : effect-system
    W! {GPU NoAlloc NoRecurse Deadline<Nms> DeterministicRNG}
    W! row-polymorphic (Koka-style)
  F4 : staged-computation
    W! scene → evaluator compile-time-specialization
    W! Futamura-2nd-projection

§ BUG-THESIS (from V5..V12 + DGI-V1..V2 retrospective)
  ∀ bug ⇒ lang-allowed-it
  W! CSSLv3 : ∀ known-bug-pattern → compile-error
  ○ CPU/GPU-SDF-divergence × 3 → effect-system F3
  ○ central-diff-perf-cliff → autodiff F1
  ○ thin-SDF-raymarch-crash → refinement F2
  ○ audio-callback-alloc-deadlock → effect F3 NoAlloc
  ○ GPU-struct-padding-corruption → refinement F2 layout-types

§ RESEARCH-SECTIONS S1..S10
  S1 : novel-langs'game+graphics
    Slang Jai Zig Vale Mojo Verse Odin Taichi Hylo/Val Circle Carbon
  S2 : compile-time-metaprogramming
    Futamura-projections Zig-comptime MetaOCaml Terra Truffle-Graal
  S3 : autodiff'systems
    Enzyme Slang.D JAX-source-xform Zygote.jl Rust-autodiff
  S4 : refinement-types
    LiquidHaskell F* Dafny Lean4 Granule QTT
  S5 : effect-systems
    Koka OCaml-5 Verse Eff Frank Multi-core-OCaml
  S6 : MLIR+codegen
    MLIR-dialects Cranelift QBE IREE SPIR-V-codegen
  S7 : engine-as-language
    GOAL GOOL UE-Verse Houdini-VEX Blueprints
  S8 : memory-models
    Vale-regions typed-arenas generational-indices
    linear-types region-calculus
  S9 : bootstrapping
    mrustc Zig-self-host OCaml-boot minimum-viable-compiler
  S10 : syntax
    APL/J-lineage dense-notation Rust-macros S-expr

§ OUTPUTS
  W! per-section : research/Sx_<topic>.csl
  W! synthesis : research/99_SYNTHESIS.csl
  W! design-manifesto : specs/00_MANIFESTO.csl
  W! bootstrap-plan : specs/01_BOOTSTRAP.csl
  W! IR-design : specs/02_IR.csl
  W! type-system : specs/03_TYPES.csl
  W! effect-system : specs/04_EFFECTS.csl
  W! autodiff : specs/05_AUTODIFF.csl
  W! staging : specs/06_STAGING.csl
  W! codegen : specs/07_CODEGEN.csl
  W! engine-primitives : specs/08_ENGINE.csl
  W! syntax : specs/09_SYNTAX.csl
  W! hw-abstraction : specs/10_HW.csl

